    "summary": "The user asks an AI assistant for help writing Instagram captions for a boutique focusing on DEI initiatives. After refining the tone, the user asks for advice on whether to address local community controversy surrounding DEI or to stick to positive messaging. The assistant advises sticking to positive messaging to avoid confrontation and maintain brand image.",
